\c 14
\nb
\v 1 UHiramu inkosi yeTire wasethuma izithunywa kuDavida, lezigodo zemisedari lababazi bamatshe lababazi bezigodo ukumakhela indlu\x + 2 Sam. 5.11-25.\x*.
\v 2 UDavida wasesazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimmisile ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli, ngoba umbuso wakhe wawuphakanyiselwe phezulu ngenxa yabantu bayo uIsrayeli.
\s Abantwana bakaDavida abazalelwa eJerusalema
\p
\v 3 UDavida wasethatha abanye abafazi eJerusalema; uDavida wasezala amanye amadodana lamadodakazi.
\v 4 Lala ngamabizo abantwana aba labo eJerusalema: OShamuwa, loShobabi, uNathani, loSolomoni,
\v 5 loIbihari, loElishuwa, loEliphaleti,
\v 6 loNoga, loNefegi, loJafiya,
\v 7 loElishama, loBeyeliyada, loElifaleti\x + 3.5-8.\x*.
\s UDavida unqoba amaFilisti
\p
\v 8 AmaFilisti esezwile ukuthi uDavida ugcotshiwe ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke, wonke amaFilisti enyuka ukudinga uDavida; uDavida ekuzwa waphuma uku\add ya\add*melana lawo\x + 2 Sam. 5.17.\x*.
\v 9 AmaFilisti asefika azisabalalisa esihotsheni seRefayimi\x + 14.13. 1 Sam. 23.27.\x*.
\v 10 UDavida wasebuza kuNkulunkulu esithi: Ngenyukele yini kumaFilisti? Uzawanikela esandleni sami yini? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Yenyuka, ngoba ngizawanikela esandleni sakho.
\v 11 Basebesenyukela eBhali-Perazimi, uDavida wawatshaya lapho; uDavida wasesithi: UNkulunkulu ufohlele ezitheni zami ngesandla sami njengokufohla kwamanzi. Ngenxa yalokhu babiza leyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiBhali-Perazimi.
\v 12 Asetshiya onkulunkulu bawo lapho, uDavida wasesithi kabatshiswe ngomlilo\x + 2 Sam. 5.21.\x*.
\v 13 AmaFilisti asebuya ezisabalalisa esihotsheni futhi.
\v 14 Lapho uDavida ebuza futhi kuNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wathi kuye: Ungenyukeli ngemva kwawo, agombolozele usuka kiwo, uze kuwo maqondana lezihlahla zebhalisamu.
\v 15 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho usizwa umsindo wokuhamba ezihlokweni zezihlahla zebhalisamu, ubusuphumela empini, ngoba uNkulunkulu uzabe esephume phambi kwakho ukutshaya ibutho lamaFilisti.
\v 16 Ngakho uDavida wenza njengoba uNkulunkulu emlayile; basebetshaya ibutho lamaFilisti kusukela eGibeyoni kwaze kwaba seGezeri.
\v 17 Njalo ibizo likaDavida laphumela kuwo wonke amazwe\x + Josh. 6.27. 2 Lan. 26.8.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasibeka ukwesabeka kwakhe phezu kwazo zonke izizwe\x + Dute. 2.25.\x*.